This is the 'gpio' package, a Linux kernel driver for the line of
general purpose input/output (GPIO) data acquisition boards made by 
MeasurementComputing (http://www.measurementcomputing.com).

This software comes with ABSOLUTELY NO WARRANTY!  See the file
'COPYING' for details.

The following boards are currently supported:

    CIO-DIO24
    PCI-DIO24
    PCI-PDISO8
    PCI-PDISO16
    PCI-DAS1000 (Digital section only)

Installation instructions can be found in the 'INSTALL' file, while full
documentation of the programming interface is in the 'API' file.
